@Node EDOPROBE "STCCG.guide/Card Extra/Edo Probe"
@rem 3.1 18.01.1998

  @{b}@{u}Edo Probe@{ub}@{uu} + Radioactive Garbage Scow
  by Dave Cain : cainda@wckn.dorm.clarkson.edu

  from @{"Alternate Universe" link "STCCG:au.guide/MAIN"}

  Seed Radioactive Garbage Scow first and then seed Edo Probe so it will
  come up as the first dilemma. If they continue with the misson they
  fail when they get to the Garbage Scow and lose the 10 points.

  Another addition to this combo would be a Destroy Radioactive Garbage
  Scow as soon as they encounter the Garbage Scow. So even if they can
  complete the mission it is worth 10 less points.

  @{b}@{u}Edo Probe@{ub}@{uu} + Cytherians
  by Jason Winter : Q@decipher.com

