  facing dilemmas. No wall dilemma need ever stop you more than a turn
  with a Countermeasure Drone on your side. Just download the necessary
  Adapt: Negate Obstruction at the end of the turn when you were stopped.
  Next turn, adapt and nullify.

  Don't always wait until trouble is staring you in the optical implants,
  though. There are several dilemmas that are particularly nasty against
  the Borg (Cytherians, for example). Make sure that only one copy of
  these bad dilemmas will bother you per game by downloading an Adapt
  with your Countermeasure Drone. Hold onto it in case you should face that
  card again.

