  Primitive Culture is irrelevant.
  Cardassian Trap is irrelevant.
  Maglock is irrelevant.

  Countermeasure Drone + Adapt: Modulate Shields:
  Phasers are irrelevant.
  Disruptors are irrelevant.
  Varon-T is irrelevant.

  Countermeasure Drone + Interlink Drone + your Hive:
  Coalescent Organisms are irrelevant.
  Alien Labyrinths are irrelevant.
  Birth of "Junior" is irrelevant.
  Ancient Computers are irrelevant.
