  hence downloading the Borg Queen. Now it's time to take over the Alpha
  Quadrant!

  Opponent's Lore + Opponent's Rogue Borg Mercenaries + FC Jean-Luc Picard:
  So, your opponent played about 6 Rogue Borg on your Enterprise-E. Use Picard
  to download Sense The Borg, and use that to download Hugh.
  Intruders? What intruders?

