  Temporal Vortex + opponent's Sheliak/Q:
  The 3 countdown is plenty of time to get out of this popular (and
  deadly) dilemma combo.

  Temporal Vortex + your Sheliak/Q:
  Keeps your opponent from using Distortion of Space/Time Continuum
  to get out of the same combo.
